QUENNE Research Institute

Quantum-Edge-Neuromorphic Engine (QUENNE)

A Research Infrastructure for Autonomous Cognitive Systems

QUENNE (Quantum-Edge-Neuromorphic Engine) is a research-grade cognitive systems architecture and open scientific initiative focused on the engineering, validation, and deployment of autonomous intelligence.

Developed by the QUENNE Research Institute (Japan), QUENNE integrates quantum probabilistic inference, neuromorphic brain-inspired learning, and real-time edge embodiment into a single, self-regulating cognitive continuum.

